Take 1 ounce each of myrrh, hepatic aloe and sarcocol gum, 3 ounces of cleaned honey, Â½ glass of good white wine and 2 drams of copper sulfate. Make powder of everything and mix it on a slow fire, always agitating it with your spatula until it is thickened in the form of an unguent. Remove it from the fire and stir and it will be made. Save it to use for your needs.

Major basic unguent.

